questions.quote: Will you get this horse outta here. He's killing me. I can't get any oxygen.
You dated her. Give me some inside information. Anything I can use!
You don't understand, Elaine. I don't want to be overanxious. If he wants to see me he has my number, he should call.
Yeah, I would. It's just, you know, I just ate a whole pot roast.
You are paying a woman to come to your house and sleep with you.
Well, there was so much snow. The roads were closed. I really appreciate it - you picking me up. Thanks again.
Let me in, it's me.  Here. You don't know what this is costing me.
Nobody carries wallets anymore. I mean, they went out with powdered wigs. Yeah, see here's what you need. Just a couple of cards and your bankroll. See, keep the big bills on the outside.
Well, you didn't hear it from me, but needless to say, if you go in there - stick with the consumee.
Sue Ellen sends me an invitation, one week before her wedding in India. Tst, I'll show her...
